    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for superior lateral dynamics. Mechanically flawless, the subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the VANOS system overhauled to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The exterior remains in factory-fresh state with zero oxidation, while the interior retains its original Nappa leather integrity. A mechanically transparent, turn-key masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
